<document>

<properties>
  <title>The constants section of the design file</title>
  <author email="jourdren@biologie.ens.fr">Laurent Jourdren</author>
</properties>

<body>

  <section name="Constants">
    <p>The design file allow the user to define constants that will be used as built-in variables:</p>
    <source>
&lt;constants&gt;
	&lt;constant&gt;
		&lt;name&gt;myconstant&lt;/name&gt;
		&lt;value&gt;200&lt;/value&gt;
	&lt;/constant&gt;
&lt;/constants&gt;
</source>

    <p>Then, you can use the constant anywhere in the design file:</p>
    <source>
	&lt;parameter&gt;
		&lt;name&gt;max&lt;/name&gt;
		&lt;value&gt;${myconstant}&lt;/value&gt;
	&lt;/parameter&lt;    
</source>
  </section>

</body>
</document>